## Caching

### Fragment Caching
```erb
<% cache @article do %>
  <%= render @article %>
<% end %>
```

### Russian Doll Caching
```erb
<% cache ['articles-list', Article.maximum(:updated_at)] do %>
  <%= render @articles %>
<% end %>
```

### Rails.cache
```ruby
Rails.cache.fetch(['article', @article.id], expires_in: 10.minutes) do
  expensive_operation
end
```

